title: GTA Online: Money Fronts
headline: GTA Online: Money Fronts
subtitle: QuickiePharm Work
content:
Make some extra cash completing deliveries in the new QuickiePharm Übermacht Sentinel GTS. Deliver emergency medical supplies in this Odd Job before the timer runs out to be rewarded with GTA$ and offered another delivery.

Successfully complete all deliveries at least five times to unlock the QuickiePharm livery for the Übermacht Sentinel GTS.

Visit your nearest QuickiePharm HQ and find the blip to start.
